{
  "stem": "24409.6",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the crew or the owner, I think, put the ship afire.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "This way it was insured.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He got his money back twice because we had paid already.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We paid as the people boarded the ship. 10 more people, 120 pounds.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Ten more people, 120 pounds.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I was standing on the bridge, and paying cash as they went on board.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And after that-- after that, I-- I think that-- put the ship afire.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "One of the sailors told it to me, that it was planned.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You know, the sailors on these ships, the [INAUDIBLE] ships-- they were not good sailors.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It-- it was the scum of the-- of all the ports in the Mediterranean.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "There's murderers and rapists and-- and people who had been in prisons for all kinds of crimes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They were the sailors.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were ready to take anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They couldn't get any jobs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were-- they were glad to have this job.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The I believe this is the last ship that I can speak today about.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The was a very good ship but the trouble was the rendezvous.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The rendezvous with the [INAUDIBLE] in the fleet, and they couldn't land.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The British ships, they were-- they chased us everywhere, but they kept to the three-mile zone.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They confiscated you only if you went within three miles. but a ship couldn't get closer than three miles.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one day the people on board every ship had been brought-- a member of the Ergon decided to land-- to-- to land anyhow, without port in Warsaw and British ordered ships.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The we broke through, straight headed for Tel Aviv Beach, and beached itself right on the center of Tel Aviv Beach.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the crowd assembled there, of course.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
